{"tid":1288040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非分化] [提防偽談判] 梁天琦：我哋一直都係反對領導嘅","createTime":"2019-07-05T12:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T13:12:11.000Z","uid":178364,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"493a7dd5a22738c0d05fe322360af231cac74bb2","tid":1288040,"uid":178364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"1:00 &quot;唔好太抬舉<span style=\"color: red;\">社會領袖或者乜人都好</span> ... ...一場示威 每一個示威者都係獨立嘅個體&quot;<br />\n1:22 &quot;我哋一直都係<span style=\"color: red;\">反對領導</span>嘅 而我哋係支持群眾自發去進行佢哋想要嘅抗爭&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_K8W-Gd75qQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_K8W-Gd75qQ&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHQDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=4632d732\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_K8W-Gd75qQ</a><br />\n<br />\n大家諗下 林鄭唔會理你啲咩條件 只要有傾過佢就會話充分聽取意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學界更加唔可以話&quot;清楚不能代表全港學生市民&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭就係知你咁講先會見其他界別 去到一個threshold就會話各界別都有諮詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時嘅分化肯定比而家大 重蹈覆轍緊學聯14年中嘅伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記唔記得學聯同政府傾咗啲乜？係乜嘢都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be067b7204500e16591974d8a8789897db194ddd","tid":1288040,"uid":148185,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:47:12.000Z","msg":"天琦既眼光真係睇得好遠<br />\n每樣野都好中point<br />\n只係當時行得太前了<br />\n香港人對唔住天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfe252117f90a9a0bb3c304dabb36bfbc3ac4c7","tid":1288040,"uid":40940,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"痴線，呢段回應好似回應緊71咁"},{"pid":"848273fdfbdfa8a99c60d955160fb50703482d2d","tid":1288040,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T12:51:06.000Z","msg":